==================Nested class=================
a class within a class in klnown as nested class
used to provide security
and when the usage of a class is only within that class then we go for inner class
they are of 4 types
	1>Inner class-a class within a class
	2>static inner class-static class within a class( behaves just like static method()
	3>anonymous inner class-a class which doesn't have name
	4>method local inner class-class class declared inside method body